secondary_street_name: Land bounded by Britannia Walk, Ebenezer Street & Westland Place
description: Redevelopment of the site through demolition of the rear of Eagle House and the retention and refurbishment of the remainder of the building together with the erection of a part 6, part 7 and part 27 storey building plus basement level to provide 276 residential units comprising 31xstudios, 69x1 bedroom, 82x2 bedroom, 65x3 bedroom, 26x4 bedroom and 3xmore than 4 bedroom units and 1271sqm of class A1 (retail) floor space, 447 sqm of class A3 (restaurant) floor space, 3486sqm of class B1(office) floorspace and 1108sqm of class D2 (Leisure) floorspace together with ancillary plant servicing, 56 basement level car parking spaces, associated hard and soft landscaping, alterations to vehicular and pedestrian access and associated highway works.
